  	<itemizedlist>
  		<listitem>Use this parameter to select which mouse button you want to click with:
  			<itemizedlist>
  				<listitem><para>1 = left mouse button</para></listitem>
  				<listitem><para>2 = middle mouse button</para></listitem>
  				<listitem><para>3 = right mouse button</para></listitem>
  			</itemizedlist>
  		</listitem>
  		<listitem><para>The mouse button you use to click with can also have an effect on what happens</para></listitem>
  		<listitem><para>The button to click will depend on your AUT and what the click should achieve.</para></listitem>
